  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink12-kilavi">uḻaiyar neruṅkik kūṟiya tiṟamum taṉatu āṟṟāmaiyum niṉaintu vāyil nērak
          karutiya talaimakaḷ parattaiyarkkup piṉpum avaṉ ciṟappuc ceytāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭup poṟāḷāyk
          karuttaḻintu taṉṉuḷḷē colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink12">
          <l> karaicēr vēḻaṅ karumpiṟ pūkkun</l>
          <l> tuṟaikē ḻūraṉ koṭumai naṉṟu</l>
          <l> māṟṟuka tilla yāmē</l>
          <l> tōṟka tillaveṉ ṟaṭameṉ ṟōḷē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l> May we bear well</l>
          <l>the cruelty of the man from the village that has a ghat</l>
          <l> where the wild cane that joins the shore flowers amongst the sugarcane!</l>
          <l> May my broad soft shoulders be defeated!</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
